```java
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException, InterruptedException {
        String imgBase64 = "";
        imgBase64 = URLEncoder.encode(imgBase64, "UTF-8");
        String accessToken = "24.8e110af52fccca5bf1b97bcdde117068.2592000.1602823822.282335-22666737";
        String baseUrl = "https://aip.baidubce.com/rest/2.0/ocr/v1/webimage";
        String url = baseUrl + "?access_token=" + accessToken + "&image=" + imgBase64;
        HttpRequest request = HttpRequest.newBuilder()
                .uri(URI.create(url))
                .header("content-type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded")
                .method("POST", HttpRequest.BodyPublishers.noBody())
                .build();
        HttpResponse<String> response = HttpClient.newHttpClient().send(request, HttpResponse.BodyHandlers.ofString());
        System.out.println(response.body());
    }
```
